snippet.title: Southfield - Release Date Announcement Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Head into a wobbly world, bounce across mushrooms, and more in Southfield. Automate, build, and explore in this farming game. 

Southfield will be released in Early Access on June 24, 2024.

#IGN #Gaming #Southfield
